    <h1>About Niki</h1>
    <div class="intro text">
        <p><i>Founder of ChangeEazy </i>and<i> Transformation Coach</i></p>
        <p>Welcome to <b>ChangeEazy</b>, where transformation meets balance. Niki, the founder of ChangeEazy and a seasoned <b>transformation coach</b>, specializes in empowering individuals and organizations to achieve peak performance through <b>personalized coaching, tailored workshops</b>, and <b>retreat programs</b>. Her holistic approach blends self-awareness, mindfulness, and change-work to help clients thrive in both personal and professional spheres.</p>
        <h2>Why Choose Niki?</h2>
        <p>With over two decades of experience working with dynamic, high-paced environments-from startups to multinational corporations-Niki understands the challenges of growth, change, and leadership. Her career spans influential roles in global organizations, including KBC, MALEV, CEU, Nikon, and Booking.com, where she built cross-cultural teams, led international projects, and drove business expansion in Europe and Asia.</p>
        <p>Her expertise is grounded in practical experience, having managed APAC operations in Singapore and scaled markets from Tokyo. Since leaving corporate life in 2014, Niki has devoted herself to helping individuals and teams unlock their potential, prevent burnout, and build resilience through <b>coaching</b>, <b>training</b>, and <b>mindfulness practices</b>.</p>
<h2>Global Reach with Local Expertise</h2>
<p>ChangeEazy collaborates with a wide network of <b>international coaches, trainers, and facilitators</b>, enabling clients to receive support in their <b>local languages</b>. This global approach ensures a culturally sensitive, personalized experience, whether you’re an individual, team, or organization.</p>
            <h2>Certifications and Expertise</h2>
            <p>Niki integrates a wide range of evidence-based methodologies into her coaching and training programs to provide actionable, lasting results. Her credentials include:</p>
            <ul><li>Certified NLP Coach and Trainer (by Dr. Richard Bandler)</li><li>Practitioner of Neuro-Hypnotic Repatterning™ and Design Human Engineering™ (by Dr. Richard Bandler)</li><li>Advanced Practitioner of the Perry Method (Patterns of Physical Transformation) (by Dr. Edie Perry)</li><li>Certified Meditation and Mindfulness Trainer</li><li>Certified Systemic Coach</li><li>Tibetan Singing Bowl Healing (certified by Shima Healing)</li><li>Advanced Practitioner of Pranic Healing and Pranic Psychotherapy (by Pranic Healing Nederland)</li></ul>
<p>Niki’s fluency in English, Dutch, and Hungarian, as well as conversational German and Russian, enables her to connect deeply with diverse audiences worldwide.</p>
<h2>Services Offered</h2>
<ul><li><b>Personalized Coaching</b>: Tailored one-on-one sessions to address personal growth, leadership, and resilience.</li><li><b>Corporate Workshops</b>: Custom-designed programs to improve team dynamics, productivity, and mental well-being.</li><li><b>Retreats</b>: Specialized coaching and mindfulness workshops for transformational experiences in serene settings.</li><li><b>Custom Trainings</b>: Unique training solutions to meet the specific needs of individuals or organizations.</li></ul>
<h2>What Sets Niki Apart?</h2>
<p>At ChangeEazy, Niki combines her deep understanding of corporate dynamics with holistic well-being practices to deliver highly effective, result-driven coaching and training programs. Her approach ensures you or your organization not only achieve your goals but also maintain a balanced and fulfilling journey.</p>
<h2>Contact Niki</h2>
    <p>Ready to take the next step in personal or professional growth? Connect with Niki at <b>ChangeEazy</b> to learn how her <b>customized coaching and training programs</b> can empower you or your organization to thrive in today’s competitive and ever-changing world.</p>
<p><b>Start your journey today</b>. </p>
<p>Balance. Performance. Change — Made Easy.</p>

